{"tid":2234081,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"去到某幾個山旮旯黨鐵站就會想爆石","createTime":"2020-10-07T14:58:17.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-08T04:59:34.000Z","uid":132193,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"02eafabb09371f5e757577b52263d257ab7abd99","tid":2234081,"uid":132193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-07T14:58:17.000Z","msg":"工作關係好多時搭黨鐵<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一去到西鐵某啲山旮旯站就會好急，港島觀塘線又無乜野<br />\n<br />\n一聽到下一站錦上路就會開始肚痛<br />\n狀態唔好時為己為人都揀唔搭巴士<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n就算有時狀態好，個肚都隨時會突然黎料<br />\n<br />\n有無人明白嗰種無助<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bark.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我係咪心理作用定咩。。。。"},{"pid":"6e68a29018d6fe33f6eacb057af5bb74286dfa84","tid":2234081,"uid":13782,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-07T15:13:54.000Z","msg":"定係其實因為港島觀塘線唔係個個站有廁所，有都得兩三格<br />\n<br />\n你自己呃自己無需要去，坐到西鐵線先認清自己其實要去<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8c3a39ba0c0fcc4afaca7fc9165fa75be969a8cb","tid":2234081,"uid":132193,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"6e68a29018d6fe33f6eacb057af5bb74286dfa84","tid":2234081,"uid":13782,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-07T15:13:54.000Z","msg":"定係其實因為港島觀塘線唔係個個站有廁所，有都得兩三格<br />\n<br />\n你自己呃自己無需要去，坐到西鐵線先認清自己其實要去<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-07T15:22:02.000Z","msg":"會唔會係郊外有種特別磁場，令人覺得舒暢啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我又無專登呃自己，但你講得無錯，我下次坐港島觀塘留意下自己個肚先"},{"pid":"a6d2147d6b848dc5650caf1f8f1e17b5f621af51","tid":2234081,"uid":75868,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-08T04:41:54.000Z","msg":"至少西鐵個個站都有廁所<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"13d722eedde4f614178963848f41d6ad8c77ad73","tid":2234081,"uid":120093,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"8c3a39ba0c0fc